-- Singh's Adviser Rangarajan Says Inflation Has Reached Uncomfortable Level
-- Anoop Agrawal
-- 2010-06-17T05:49:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/singh-s-adviser-rangarajan-says-inflation-has-reached-uncomfortable-level.html

          
          
             India’s inflation has reached an
“uncomfortable” level, Chakravarthy Rangarajan, chairman of
the Prime Minister’s Economic Advisory Council, said in Mumbai
today.  
